Hi, Alessandro,

I have confirmed and reproduced your error.

It should be a bug and it is in
https://github.com/RcppCore/Rcpp/blob/master/inst/include/Rcpp/vector/MatrixColumn.h#L39

In your case, i and n both are integers, but i * n caused an overflow. We
will fix this soon.

Thank you for the test on big vector and matrix. More test will be truly
appreciated.

Best wishes,

KK

